Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.33,0:00:03.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Suspense and deduction\Ncloses the gap between
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.73,0:00:07.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In a beautiful garden a mysterious\Ncase occurs
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.77,0:00:09.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He sees through the one and only truth
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.47,0:00:10.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,a child in appearance\Nwith the I.Q. of an adult
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.14,0:00:13.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,nojcase is left unsolved\Nwith Detective Conan.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.55,0:02:02.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you for the treat
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.62,0:02:05.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Gee... This is such a great\Ngarden that's true to your title
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.25,0:02:08.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,as the president of\Nthe Kiyama Furniture Company
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.32,0:02:11.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What a nice house you have!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.26,0:02:14.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is the first time I've seen\Na garden with a waterfall like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.20,0:02:16.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This garden somehow\Nmakes me feel at peace
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.93,0:02:19.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Glad to hear that...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.94,0:02:20.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You like my garden.\NI'm glad I brought you up here too.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.20,0:02:20.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You like my garden.\NI'm glad I brought you up here too.\NMichiyoshi Majima
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.60,0:02:24.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,you like my garden.\NI'm glad I brought you up here too.\NMichiyoshi Majima\NDI DI all.Â»\NO v9 fr C Let)\NXLRI MR
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.84,0:02:25.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,you like my garden.\NI'm glad I brought you up here too.\NLe & &UL\Nw PF fr CC LoTOoD\NKIRA T=
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.07,0:02:25.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,you like my garden.\NI'm glad I brought you up here too.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.34,0:02:29.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I think it's about time to begin
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.88,0:02:31.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Eh? To begin what?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.95,0:02:34.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You'll see.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.19,0:02:40.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, Conan, look over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.49,0:02:43.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Water is flowing over\Nthe basin of the waterfall!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.09,0:02:44.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Clio, Tl
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.43,0:02:47.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The water is filling the garden!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.40,0:02:49.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's that!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.70,0:02:52.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hahaha Surprised. eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.90,0:02:53.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let me explain how this works.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.97,0:02:59.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,At 8am... 4 p.m. and 8 p.m. three times\Na day, the water flows into the garden
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.74,0:03:03.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But in doing so,\Nwon't the{\rHonorifics - Dialogue} san{\r}d pattern disappear?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.71,0:03:06.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Water is poured in slowly\Nso that the pattern is not lost,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.72,0:03:09.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,then the water is drained in 30 minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.35,0:03:14.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's quite highly reputed.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.19,0:03:16.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The former president made this device.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.33,0:03:21.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, if you'll excuse me for a moment,\NI'd like to get back to work
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.83,0:03:24.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But make yourselves at home.\NSee you at dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.30,0:03:27.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And don't worry about your car.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.17,0:03:29.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll get my secretary to pick it up tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.57,0:03:32.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank so much for everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.61,0:03:35.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sure you'd have done the same for me\Nif I were in your shoes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.58,0:03:38.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,OK then. I'll leave them to you, Ayaka.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.25,0:03:40.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Very well, President...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.38,0:03:42.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Boy oh boy, what ajtruly superb view!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.85,0:03:44.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's really awesome...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.75,0:03:48.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Heck! What carefree jokers they are!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.39,0:03:49.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't they realize how costly\Nit is to maintain it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.03,0:03:53.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The garden Kiyama made is\Nreally nothing but a big nuisance for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.83,0:03:57.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Look, Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.37,0:04:02.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, my, we can see clearly through\Nthe circles of white{\rHonorifics - Dialogue} san{\r}d!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.80,0:04:05.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's beautiful, Ran!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.57,0:04:08.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll bet it's especially romanticsat night\Nwhen the moon is reflected on the water
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.94,0:04:11.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.08,0:04:15.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We even have guests\Nwho come here every full moon.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.75,0:04:21.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wonderful to drink cold sake while viewing\Na full moon rising from behind Mt. Fuji
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.96,0:04:28.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Phew!\NIt's out of this world...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.00,0:04:29.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, what's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.23,0:04:32.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Over there. Something's by the pillar...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.77,0:04:35.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, that! It's a catching pole.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.10,0:04:36.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Catching pole?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.57,0:04:43.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You see, when someone drops\Nsomething on the white{\rHonorifics - Dialogue} san{\r}d of the yard,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.51,0:04:46.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,we lengthen this pole\Nand pick it up like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.65,0:04:51.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We can't step on the wave pattern\Nof the white{\rHonorifics - Dialogue} san{\r}d, you see.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.49,0:04:54.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see. It's well thought out.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.36,0:04:55.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.42,0:05:00.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,since Mr. Majima became president, the -\Ngardener comes only once a month. So...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.03,0:05:01.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Pretty mind racking, isn't it...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.73,0:05:02.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Pretty mind racking, isn't it...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.93,0:05:06.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, the water's begun to drain.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.87,0:05:07.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, really.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.04,0:05:14.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, It's amazing how well this works...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.31,0:05:19.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,VA. AA.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.75,0:05:24.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,HA AA\NMystery of the Japanese Water\NFlowing Rock Garden Part
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.39,0:05:31.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you like, shall we go to the saloon
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.19,0:05:33.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,where aperitif will be served
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.86,0:05:36.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah, here we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.67,0:05:44.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You don't have money!?
