Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.26,0:06:40.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, thank you, thank you
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.76,0:06:42.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's the man we saw just a while ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.86,0:06:43.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.70,0:06:46.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Can I get you something to drink, sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.33,0:06:48.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sure, I'll take a beer!
