Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.31,0:06:58.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who're these people!?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.28,0:07:00.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They are Mr. Majima's guests.
