Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.45,0:07:05.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't know if we can be called guest,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.09,0:07:11.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,because you see, we\Nactually ran out of gas on Sanbonzaka
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.33,0:07:17.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, President Majima, who\Nhappened to pass by, looked in on us.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.13,0:07:22.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Moreover, he kindly invited us\Nfor dinner this evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.70,0:07:27.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The president is a nice\Nfriendly person, isn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.74,0:07:31.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Heck! He always puts\Non a friendly face in public!
