Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.52,0:07:44.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All is well, Mr. Endo.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.63,0:07:46.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mr. Majima invited them...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.96,0:07:50.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And besides.\NThe more the merrier for dinner, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.37,0:07:51.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I guess so, but...
