Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.75,0:08:03.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nice to meet you .
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.95,0:08:06.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And this is the president of\Nthe Kiyama Interior Company,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.48,0:08:08.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,one of our affiliated\Ncompanies, Mr. Endo
