Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.76,0:08:15.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's something!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.96,0:08:16.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But it was long time ago.\NNow, it's a different story...
