Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.00,0:08:21.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And I'm Tomonori Kiyama,\Na freelance writer.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.33,0:08:24.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And I'm Tomonori Kiyama,\Na freelance writer.\NTomonori Kiyama\NKL 8 AY (28)\NDI-- SS
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.74,0:08:31.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you Mr. Kiyama, the author of\NWandering Through Africa?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.81,0:08:32.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.27,0:08:34.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wow! I thought so!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.68,0:08:36.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do you know him?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.64,0:08:40.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah! He is a travelogue writer\Nwho travels to many countries.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.85,0:08:43.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've read your\NWandering Through Africa!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.59,0:08:45.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, thank you
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.59,0:08:47.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How did you like it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.05,0:08:49.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh...I was deeply moved!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.86,0:08:53.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could I have your autograph,please?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.50,0:08:55.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sure, my pleasure!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.56,0:08:56.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I tell you what
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.33,0:08:59.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll be holding a photo exhibition
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.30,0:09:01.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So if it's okay with you, please come.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.50,0:09:04.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wow! Thank you, are you sure it's okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.27,0:09:06.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.57,0:09:09.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll sign my autograph now...
