Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.09,0:09:21.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Although it's no great fountain pen
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.79,0:09:25.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I just couldn't bear getting rid of it\NSo, I always keep it on me
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.76,0:09:26.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see .
