Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.91,0:09:43.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My father built the company\Nfrom nothing into
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.14,0:09:44.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,a considerable business In\Nthe course of his lifetime.
