Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.85,0:09:55.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, we have! Patterns on the\Nwhite{\rHonorifics - Dialogue} san{\r}d were so beautiful!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.19,0:09:59.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Exactly! That waterfall and white{\rHonorifics - Dialogue} san{\r}d!\NThe garden you saw
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.36,0:10:01.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,was what my father kept working on to\Ncomplete, whenever he had time
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.96,0:10:03.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,to spare from his busy schedule,\Nputting his heart and soul into it.
