Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.86,0:10:27.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.96,0:10:30.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's very beautiful.\NAll of you really must see it
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.09,0:10:32.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shall we go up there, Conan!
