Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.17,0:13:59.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hm...Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.23,0:14:01.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, please talk this over with your father
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.24,0:14:02.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,before you decide whether you\Nwant to buy it or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.34,0:14:11.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you'll excuse me, I'veggot to get going\Nsince I still have work: left to do...
