Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.82,0:14:21.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,OK, listen, I have a video\Nthat I want to watch,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.12,0:14:22.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,so I hope you don't mind going to see\Nthe night view after I'm done.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.49,0:14:24.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sure, no problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.36,0:14:28.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, I'll come and pick you up\Naround eleven fifteen.
