Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.66,0:16:08.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But once he gets you,\Nyou can't get rid of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.83,0:16:14.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's his way so don't get involved\Nwith him! He's bad news!
